{"tid":1772781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波料數年經濟環境困難　持開放態度研是否派錢紓困","createTime":"2019-12-07T02:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:00:53.000Z","uid":208505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"692f1f6880c154f5844a440966fb00a82ea36a61","tid":1772781,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府推出第四輪紓困措施，其中分期繳稅的申請安排被批評手續繁複。財政司司長陳茂波指，有人曾提議延期半年交稅，但政府認為做法不可行。 <br />\n<br />\n陳茂波預計，未來數年經濟環境也困難，可能不僅一年，財政預算出現赤字，要顧慮政府長遠承擔能力，會持開放態度研究是否派錢紓困，但他提到上次派四千元的關愛共享計劃有不完善的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=372535&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372535%26refer%3DShare&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=38b05c90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372535%26refer%3DShare&h=12bdf9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=372535&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">派錢好丫，洗係黃色經濟圈身上,用黎買gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,拎黎捐去外國遊說團隊，間接支持呢場運動</span>"},{"pid":"32ef70d27838444183153e155aa420dccfc87e1b","tid":1772781,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"派一年都未派完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c647e9a670c650c33ba9a1d02539bbc122998e","tid":1772781,"uid":57549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"又洗三億行政費去派一億比新移民"},{"pid":"ad25b1a5cdb1714c0661a4f153d240cdf3c8f504","tid":1772781,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"還掂都捐輸俾中共<br />\n港共派1蚊都照攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}